('73784','25580','5','Newly built luxury villa with stunning sea views in Portals Nous'),
('73785','25581','5','Portals Nous is one of the "hot spots" in the southwest of Mallorca. The proximity to the exclusive marina of Puerto Portals with its first-class restaurants and bars, to the Royal Golf Course of Bendinat, international schools and the island’s capital Palma is the reason why this place is one of the most sought-after residential areas in Mallorca.\r\nThe modern-style luxury villa has been finished in 2013 to a very high standard and offers 4 bedrooms which provide enough space for up to 8 people. The 1,800 m² plot is located directly at the beach of Portals Nous. Restaurants, supermarkets and the international King Richard College are within walking distance.\r\nThe living area of approx. 710 m² is distributed at 3 floors. Entering the villa on the ground floor there is a bright entrance hall with an imposing stairway. On this floor you have 2 spacious master suites with terrace overlooking the sea, two guest bedrooms each with en suite bathrooms, and an office room. Travelling down the wide elegant stairway you will find the living room with large panoramic windows and terrace. The ample modern kitchen with appliances by Gaggenau and Miele, will be heaven on earth for every hobby chef. Furthermore, on this level is situated a cozy fireplace lounge and a home theatre. On the basement level one can create further guest rooms or a spa area with fitness room. A bathroom with shower and toilet has already been installed. The installation of borrowed lights has been prepared.\r\nThe quality home is of superior construction offering many special features such as under floor heating throughout (oil), air conditioning h / c, double glazed windows and automatic irrigation system. In the beautifully kept garden is a carport which provides parking space for 2 cars.'),
